description: Enjoy the best R&B hits from the nineties & zeroes! Old school RnB classics and throwback party jams from TLC, Usher, Aaliyah, Chris Brown, Mario, Jennifer Lopez, Drake, Ne-Yo, Alicia Keys, Destiny's Child, Mariah Carey, Nelly, and more. Throwback RnB party | Club Bangers | Smooth Vibes Only
